org.cpsolver.instructor.model

Class InstructorSchedulingModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Model<TeachingRequest.Variable,TeachingAssignment>
      • org.cpsolver.instructor.model.InstructorSchedulingModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Test

    public class InstructorSchedulingModel
extends Model<TeachingRequest.Variable,TeachingAssignment>
    Instructor Scheduling Model. Variables are TeachingRequest, values are TeachingAssignment. Each teaching request has a course (see Course) and one or more sections (see {link Section}). Each assignment assigns one instructor (see Instructor) to a single teaching request.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Instructor Sectioning)
